                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Activate focused button or link</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr class="hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800">
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 whitespace-nowrap">
                                    <kbd class="px-2 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-600 rounded">Esc</kbd>
                                </td>
                                <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">Close modals or dialogs</td>
                            </tr>
                        </tbody>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </TbCard>
        </section>

        <!-- Common Tasks -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Common Tasks</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <!-- Task Card 1 -->
                <TbCard>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Reset All Settings to Default</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-3">
                        If you want to restore all settings to their default values:
                    </p>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                        <li>Go to <a href="/settings" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Settings</a></li>
                        <li>Scroll to the bottom of the page</li>
                        <li>Click the "Reset to Defaults" button</li>
                        <li>Confirm the action in the dialog</li>
                    </ol>
                </TbCard>

                <!-- Task Card 2 -->
                <TbCard>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">View Trade History</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-3">
                        To review your past trades and analyze performance:
                    </p>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                        <li>Navigate to the <a href="/portfolio" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Portfolio</a> page</li>
                        <li>Scroll down to the "Trade History" section</li>
                        <li>Use filters to narrow down trades by date or symbol</li>
                        <li>Click on any trade for detailed information</li>
                    </ol>
                </TbCard>

                <!-- Task Card 3 -->
                <TbCard>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Run a Backtest</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-3">
                        To test a strategy against historical data:
                    </p>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                        <li>Go to the <a href="/backtest" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Backtesting</a> page</li>
                        <li>Select a strategy from the dropdown</li>
                        <li>Choose a date range for historical data</li>
                        <li>Click "Run Backtest" to start the simulation</li>
                        <li>Review results and performance metrics</li>
                    </ol>
                </TbCard>

                <!-- Task Card 4 -->
                <TbCard>
                    <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">Monitor Live Performance</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-3">
                        To track your trading performance in real-time:
                    </p>
                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 space-y-1">
                        <li>Visit the <a href="/performance" class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline">Performance</a> page</li>
                        <li>View your equity curve chart</li>
                        <li>Check key metrics (Sharpe Ratio, Max Drawdown, etc.)</li>
                        <li>Adjust date range to see historical performance</li>
                    </ol>
                </TbCard>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Troubleshooting -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Troubleshooting</h2>
            <TbCard>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">My settings are not saving</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1 text-sm">
                            Make sure you click the "Save Changes" button after modifying your settings. If the problem persists, check your browser console for errors and ensure you have a stable internet connection.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Dashboard data is not updating</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1 text-sm">
                            Check your dashboard refresh interval in Settings. If it's set too high (e.g., 300 seconds), you may not see frequent updates. Try reducing it to 5-10 seconds. Also ensure your internet connection is stable.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">I'm not receiving notifications</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1 text-sm">
                            Go to Settings and verify that the notification types you want to see are enabled. Check that the notification duration is set to at least 2 seconds so you have time to read them.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">The page layout looks broken</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mt-1 text-sm">
                            TradingBot is optimized for desktop screens with a minimum width of 1024px. If you're on a smaller screen or mobile device, some features may not display correctly. Please use a desktop or laptop computer for the best experience.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </TbCard>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Support -->
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Need More Help?</h2>
            <TbCard>
                <div class="text-center py-6">
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                        Can't find what you're looking for? Contact your system administrator for additional support.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </TbCard>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

